## 🔌 Supported LLM Providers

| Provider | Model | Status |
|----------|-------|--------|
| OpenAI | gpt-4, gpt-3.5-turbo | ✅ |
| Anthropic | claude-3-opus, claude-3-sonnet | ✅ |
| Ollama | llama2, mistral, etc. | ✅ |
| Azure OpenAI | gpt-4, gpt-3.5-turbo | ✅ |

